40:16.834 --> 40:17.835
-[assistant] Hi.
-[Jodi] Hi.

40:17.918 --> 40:20.337
-How was your ride?
-Yeah. It was great.

40:20.420 --> 40:21.421
[Megan] It was good.

40:21.505 --> 40:23.090
I'm Helen.
