40:24.675 --> 40:25.717
[Megan] Thank you.

40:30.264 --> 40:32.933
So it's a total pattern.
A pattern of behavior.

40:33.016 --> 40:35.769
Gwyneth was invited to the hotel room,
the business meeting,

40:35.853 --> 40:38.689
and then threatened with losing her job
if she refused him.

40:38.772 --> 40:41.483
She told her agent. No one does a thing.

40:41.567 --> 40:43.110
[Rebecca] Will Gwyneth go on the record?

40:43.819 --> 40:44.820
She really wants to.

40:44.903 --> 40:46.530
I think she does and she doesn't.

40:46.613 --> 40:51.243
She is scared that it could turn into
some kind of tabloidy sex scandal.

40:51.326 --> 40:55.706
I mean, Gwyneth was 23. So was Rose.
They were so young.

40:55.789 --> 40:57.708
[Rebecca]
Tell me everything when you get in.

40:57.791 --> 40:59.042
Okay. Bye.

41:01.336 --> 41:02.504
[sighs]

41:03.589 --> 41:06.633
The only way these women
are gonna go on the record…

41:06.717 --> 41:07.843
Is if they all jump together.

41:09.219 --> 41:10.220
Yeah.

41:18.562 --> 41:20.689
[doorbell rings]

41:20.772 --> 41:22.524
You take the lead on this.

41:22.608 --> 41:25.110
No, you do it.
You're less intimidating.

41:25.194 --> 41:27.112
You don't find me intimidating?

41:28.697 --> 41:31.366
-I mean-- No, it's just the height thing.
-[door opens]

41:32.159 --> 41:33.577
-Hi.
-[Jodi] Hi.

41:33.660 --> 41:35.704
We were just
in the neighborhood.

41:35.787 --> 41:37.206
We're from
The New York Times.

41:37.289 --> 41:39.708
I believe you used to work
for Harvey Weinstein?

41:43.504 --> 41:44.796
[door closes]

41:46.632 --> 41:48.467
-Think she'll go on the record?
-[laughs]

41:49.426 --> 41:50.928
Okay. I'm just gonna…

41:51.011 --> 41:52.930
[Megan] You wanna leave the note? Yeah.

42:02.523 --> 42:05.192
The NDAs are never examined or questioned.

42:05.275 --> 42:08.445
They rarely come up in open court.
Law schools don't teach them.

42:08.529 --> 42:10.781
Also, the attorneys
who represent the victims

42:10.864 --> 42:13.116
can get up to 40% of the settlement.

42:13.200 --> 42:15.285
That's a big incentive
to keep that system going.

42:15.369 --> 42:18.121
Most sexual harassment cases
are settled out of court.

42:18.205 --> 42:20.624
And most of them
have a confidentiality clause.

42:20.707 --> 42:24.002
And the women who sign these contracts
have to give over all of their evidence.

42:24.086 --> 42:26.255
Their diaries, emails, phones.

42:26.338 --> 42:29.800
It's cash for silence, and it enables
the perpetrators to continue.

42:29.883 --> 42:32.261
[Megan]
And these clauses are standard practice.

42:32.344 --> 42:35.222
The women wanna close the case.
They need the money.

42:35.305 --> 42:37.975
They don't wanna be branded
as liars or flirts.

42:38.058 --> 42:40.978
I mean, I'm sure it often seems like
the only recourse.

42:41.061 --> 42:44.898
And I imagine some women see these
settlements as a confession of guilt.

42:44.982 --> 42:48.777
They think they've scored a victory
when it's actually a gag order.

42:48.861 --> 42:50.988
And if you try and take
a case like this to court,

42:51.071 --> 42:53.115
the sexual harassment laws
are so weak.

42:53.198 --> 42:55.325
They're actually nonexistent
if you're a freelancer

42:55.409 --> 42:57.578
or if there are fewer than
15 employees in the workplace.

42:57.661 --> 42:59.454
Also,
most lawyers prefer settlements

42:59.538 --> 43:01.331
'cause it's less of a financial risk
for them.

43:01.415 --> 43:04.710
How close are any of these actresses
to going on the record?

43:04.793 --> 43:06.920
We're introducing the idea.

43:07.004 --> 43:09.882
I'm afraid we have
these horrific hotel room accounts

43:09.965 --> 43:12.050
and no corroborating evidence.

43:12.134 --> 43:16.346
We feel they'll speak out
if they're not the only ones.

43:16.430 --> 43:17.681
Safety in numbers.

43:17.764 --> 43:18.765
And settlements?

43:19.433 --> 43:21.727
Three. So far.

43:21.810 --> 43:23.770
There is Rose McGowan.

43:23.854 --> 43:26.315
We're pretty sure about
Ambra Battilana.

43:26.398 --> 43:28.901
And I would say the same
for the ex-assistant in Queens.

43:28.984 --> 43:30.319
And no documents?

43:30.402 --> 43:32.863
We do not have
a publishable story.

43:37.534 --> 43:38.577
Hey.

43:38.660 --> 43:40.245
[Dean] So, look, team.

43:40.829 --> 43:44.333
You have to imagine that every call
you make is being recorded.

43:44.416 --> 43:45.876
And you're being followed.

43:46.543 --> 43:49.254
Don't let Weinstein talk to you,
unless it's on the record.

43:50.255 --> 43:53.425
I'd be interested in talking to him
even off the record.

43:53.509 --> 43:58.013
No, if Harvey has something to say,
he needs to say it publicly.

43:58.096 --> 44:00.015
I've dealt with him before.

44:00.098 --> 44:01.350
It's ugly.

44:03.352 --> 44:06.688
[Megan] We're looking into the incident
with Ambra Battilana Gutierrez.

44:07.272 --> 44:09.566
She accused Weinstein of groping her.

44:09.650 --> 44:12.694
The NYPD gave her a wire,
and she met him again.

44:12.778 --> 44:14.404
[Jodi] But the DA wouldn't prosecute.

44:15.239 --> 44:17.741
They claimed the recording
wasn't enough to arrest him.

44:17.824 --> 44:21.578
[Megan] Linda Fairstein worked
in the DA's office. I've texted her.

44:23.497 --> 44:25.207
-[Ambra]
-[Harvey]

45:58.467 --> 46:00.469
Linda, Megan Twohey here.
How are you?

46:01.011 --> 46:03.138
[Linda] I'm good, Megan.
How can I help?

46:03.222 --> 46:06.642
Yeah, I'm looking into a police complaint
against Harvey Weinstein

46:06.725 --> 46:08.310
that wasn't charged. Two years ago.

46:08.393 --> 46:10.395
When you were at the DA's office.

46:10.479 --> 46:12.773
Ambra Battilana Gutierrez.

46:12.856 --> 46:14.816
Oh. Okay.

46:15.526 --> 46:17.361
It seemed to go away very quickly.

46:18.612 --> 46:20.155
There was no criminal conduct there.

46:20.239 --> 46:23.283
The cops seemed pretty confident
there was.

46:24.284 --> 46:26.995
Do you think there was anything irregular
about how it was handled?

46:27.579 --> 46:30.207
-I don't. Why would you say that?
-[sirens wailing]

46:30.290 --> 46:32.251
[cell phone ringing]

46:33.001 --> 46:34.002
Gwyneth.

46:34.086 --> 46:37.965
He's here. I invited a few people over,
and he turned up.

46:38.674 --> 46:42.010
I haven't seen him for years.
He must know I spoke to you.

46:42.094 --> 46:45.013
Why are you so certain
there was no criminal conduct?

46:45.097 --> 46:46.306
Wasn't there a recording?

46:48.308 --> 46:49.935
I don't think
there's a road to go down.

46:50.561 --> 46:51.895
No.

46:51.979 --> 46:54.398
Do you feel like
you're in physical danger at all?

46:54.481 --> 46:56.775
[Gwyneth] I'll keep people around me
till he goes.

46:56.859 --> 46:59.111
It's a shock.
I know he's watching me.

46:59.194 --> 47:00.237
He's letting me know.

47:01.697 --> 47:03.198
He can't do anything.

47:04.032 --> 47:06.910
Gwyneth. I'm here. Call me if you need me.

47:07.744 --> 47:08.745
Okay. Bye.

47:11.206 --> 47:13.166
Linda, do you know Harvey?

47:13.876 --> 47:15.169
I've met him socially,

47:15.252 --> 47:17.379
but we've never been
to each other's homes.

47:18.088 --> 47:21.717
-Okay. I'm sure we'll speak soon.
-Yes.

47:22.467 --> 47:23.468
Goodbye.

47:29.183 --> 47:32.060
We got a good lead to talk
to a past executive at Miramax.

47:32.144 --> 47:33.729
-Great. When will that be?
-[patron 1] Hola.

47:33.812 --> 47:35.147
Jodi's talking to her tomorrow.

47:35.230 --> 47:37.983
[patron 2] I don't think she heard you.
She definitely didn't hear you.

47:38.066 --> 47:39.943
-Oh, my God.
-What?

47:41.820 --> 47:46.283
Ronan Farrow is working on an HW piece
for The New Yorker.

47:46.366 --> 47:48.035
What? Since when?

47:48.118 --> 47:49.203
-[Jodi] She doesn't say…
-Fuck.

47:49.286 --> 47:51.914
…but apparently
he's spoken to a lot of actresses already.

47:52.873 --> 47:53.957
[waiter] Okay, ladies.

47:54.041 --> 47:55.667
These are the menus.

47:55.751 --> 47:57.085
-Thank you.
-[Rebecca] Thank you.

47:57.961 --> 48:00.839
It's pressure we can do without,
but we just keep going.

48:00.923 --> 48:02.841
And we continue to be thorough.

48:02.925 --> 48:04.468
Pardon me. Excuse me.
Hello.

48:04.551 --> 48:05.969
Hi. Hello, everyone.

48:06.053 --> 48:08.514
Did you see my friend over there?
He said hi.

48:08.597 --> 48:10.516
Could you leave us?
We're talking.

48:10.599 --> 48:12.684
I absolutely will.
I totally understand,

48:12.768 --> 48:14.353
but I was thinking
maybe I could have a moment--

48:14.436 --> 48:16.313
We're having a conversation.
So if you could just--

48:16.396 --> 48:18.732
-You should be doing something else.
-[Megan] Fuck you.

48:18.815 --> 48:22.319
-Fuck you? I would bend you over--
-Fuck you!

48:23.403 --> 48:25.531
Fuck you!
Get the fuck out of here!

48:25.614 --> 48:27.157
Fuck you, man.
Get the fuck out!

48:27.241 --> 48:28.909
[laughs]

48:30.661 --> 48:33.330
-[patron 1] Frigid bitches.
-[patron 2] Frigid bitches.

48:33.413 --> 48:35.165
[patron 3] That guy's an asshole.

48:35.249 --> 48:37.000
-[Megan whispers] Sorry.
-Don't apologize.

48:46.844 --> 48:48.345
[chattering]

48:52.850 --> 48:57.229
[Miramax executive] There was an incident
in Venice at the Film Festival.

48:57.312 --> 48:59.273
It was '98.

48:59.982 --> 49:01.525
What happened?

49:05.279 --> 49:08.782
What makes me most angry
is the silence.

49:09.408 --> 49:12.953
No one spoke out then,
and no one is talking about it now.

49:13.829 --> 49:16.832
He built the silence,
and people complied.

49:17.416 --> 49:19.877
He produced fear
and intimidation.

49:19.960 --> 49:22.462
The only alternative,
seemingly, was to quit

49:22.546 --> 49:25.924
and throw away everything
you worked so hard for out the door.

49:26.008 --> 49:28.385
You were terrified
you were gonna be the next target,

49:28.468 --> 49:30.053
so people looked the other way.

49:30.137 --> 49:31.138
Within the company?

49:31.221 --> 49:32.806
Yes, and outside of it.

49:33.515 --> 49:36.143
I mean, he played the press.
He played the agents.

49:36.226 --> 49:37.978
How did he play the press?

49:38.061 --> 49:42.441
By promising them access to stars
in exchange for hushing up some incident.

49:42.524 --> 49:43.692
What sort of incident?

49:45.110 --> 49:46.278
Where do I start?

49:47.237 --> 49:49.448
Harvey had this--
What did they call it?

49:50.240 --> 49:54.995
"A physical altercation"
with a male employee at a conference.

49:55.579 --> 49:57.122
Then they settled with the guy.

49:57.873 --> 49:59.291
And with women?

50:00.626 --> 50:01.627
He pursued them.

50:02.794 --> 50:03.962
Endlessly.

50:07.716 --> 50:09.635
What happened in Venice?

50:11.762 --> 50:14.556
I don't wanna be quoted. Period.

50:15.307 --> 50:16.475
Understood.

50:20.604 --> 50:22.231
We were in Harvey's suite,

50:22.314 --> 50:24.691
and there were
a bunch of people in there.

50:25.275 --> 50:29.696
And there were these two assistants,
and they were sitting there trembling.

50:30.447 --> 50:32.157
And Weinstein was there?

50:32.241 --> 50:33.283
Yes.

50:34.409 --> 50:36.912
He was talking film
and ignoring them,

50:37.996 --> 50:39.998
but they were literally vibrating.

50:40.874 --> 50:44.211
One with fear,
the other with anger.

50:46.547 --> 50:47.965
Can you tell me their names?

50:49.132 --> 50:50.217
Yes.

50:55.514 --> 50:58.433
And there's another woman
you should call.

50:59.560 --> 51:02.771
The two assistants are Rowena Chiu
and Zelda Perkins,

51:02.855 --> 51:05.899
and we have a third name,
Laura Madden.

51:05.983 --> 51:08.694
And none of them are returning our calls.

51:08.777 --> 51:10.487
So? Show up in person.

51:11.071 --> 51:12.573
Yeah. [chuckles]

51:13.115 --> 51:17.202
They live in London,
Silicon Valley and Wales.

51:17.828 --> 51:19.288
Can you get on a plane?

51:26.587 --> 51:29.131
Let me work it out with Ron.

51:32.509 --> 51:34.845
But yeah, of course.

51:34.928 --> 51:38.432
Documents, verification.
You know what we need.

52:22.601 --> 52:23.602
Hi.

52:24.561 --> 52:27.064
Sorry to bother you.
I can see you're busy.

52:27.147 --> 52:29.399
I was looking for Rowena Chiu.

52:30.484 --> 52:31.735
Hi.

52:31.818 --> 52:35.197
