Can I give her a message?

52:35.906 --> 52:37.282
When will she be back?

52:37.366 --> 52:40.452
My wife's out of the country for a while.

52:40.536 --> 52:41.537
[chuckles] I see.

52:42.162 --> 52:44.206
I did try calling her.

52:44.289 --> 52:45.666
This a work thing?

52:45.749 --> 52:46.750
No.

52:46.834 --> 52:49.211
You must be Andrew?
Andrew Cheung?

52:49.294 --> 52:51.797
I'm Jodi Kantor.
I'm from The New York Times.

52:51.880 --> 52:53.048
Okay.

52:53.924 --> 52:56.552
So, what did you wanna
talk to Rowena about?

52:57.553 --> 53:00.806
We're researching a story
about Miramax.

53:00.889 --> 53:02.891
I flew in from New York.

53:03.600 --> 53:05.853
-You came all this way?
-Yeah.

53:07.479 --> 53:09.898
Um, could we talk for a minute?

53:10.524 --> 53:11.525
Sure.

53:12.192 --> 53:17.155
So, I've been speaking with people
who worked for Harvey Weinstein.

53:18.115 --> 53:20.868
You're going quite far back
with Rowena's time there.

53:21.451 --> 53:23.787
We're writing about
his treatment of women.

53:23.871 --> 53:25.080
Right.

53:25.163 --> 53:27.457
And Rowena fits in how?

53:29.251 --> 53:32.504
Your wife worked at Miramax
for some years.

53:33.338 --> 53:36.216
Yes. Mainly in Hong Kong.

53:36.800 --> 53:39.636
I'd like to hear about her experiences
working for Weinstein.

53:40.554 --> 53:42.598
I'm confused why you can't discuss it
on the phone.

53:42.681 --> 53:43.807
[laughs]

53:43.891 --> 53:47.186
I did try.
It is always better to actually meet.

53:50.230 --> 53:51.356
So…

53:53.066 --> 53:55.152
And this is off the record.

53:56.153 --> 53:57.487
My understanding is that--

53:58.322 --> 54:00.199
that Weinstein possibly
victimized your wife

54:00.282 --> 54:01.867
when Rowena first worked for him.

54:05.662 --> 54:08.749
Rowena's never mentioned
anything like that to me.

54:09.583 --> 54:12.628
What do you mean by "victimized"?
Can you be more specific?

54:14.254 --> 54:18.133
I was told that your wife may have
received a settlement from Weinstein.

54:19.009 --> 54:22.221
[scoffs] Do I look like a guy
whose wife got a settlement?

54:23.972 --> 54:26.433
Could you have confused her
with someone else?

54:26.517 --> 54:29.770
I apologize for taking up your time. I'm--

54:30.479 --> 54:32.773
Would you just please give this to Rowena?

54:33.690 --> 54:37.027
If you're talking to these other people,
why do you need to talk to Rowena?

54:37.653 --> 54:41.323
And if you turn up in my driveway,
what kind of victimization?

54:42.366 --> 54:43.450
It's complex.

54:43.534 --> 54:45.786
I'm asking you to expand on it.

54:46.370 --> 54:49.289
I really think it would be best…

54:50.791 --> 54:52.626
if you asked Rowena.

54:52.709 --> 54:54.127
Have a good day.

55:02.636 --> 55:04.096
[engine starts]

55:07.307 --> 55:09.226
[Jodi] I just couldn't lie to him.

55:09.309 --> 55:10.894
And then it turns out he didn't know.

55:11.645 --> 55:13.438
What if London is a repeat of this?

55:13.522 --> 55:14.690
It won't be.

55:15.274 --> 55:17.359
I spoke with an employment lawyer
in the UK

55:17.442 --> 55:20.821
and he told me
that it was irresponsible of me

55:20.904 --> 55:22.865
even to ask about
breaching NDAs.

55:22.948 --> 55:24.408
No one does it.
They would get sued.

55:24.491 --> 55:26.201
Fuck that guy.

55:26.285 --> 55:28.537
Honestly, Jodi, fuck him. He has no idea.

55:29.371 --> 55:31.248
I wish I smoked or something.

55:32.249 --> 55:35.169
