55:35.252 --> 55:37.296
and all I can think is, "Fuck."

55:37.379 --> 55:38.589
That's okay.

55:39.715 --> 55:40.716
Fuck.

55:41.383 --> 55:43.552
And documents.

55:53.145 --> 55:54.479
So, Laura,

55:54.563 --> 55:57.191
we are looking
at a full mastectomy.

55:57.274 --> 55:59.943
And we should schedule this
as soon as possible.

56:01.195 --> 56:02.696
I understand.

56:07.701 --> 56:09.369
[line ringing]

56:12.414 --> 56:13.665
[Laura] Hello.

56:13.749 --> 56:15.000
Hi.

56:15.083 --> 56:17.920
Laura, this is Jodi Kantor
from The New York Times.

56:18.003 --> 56:20.547
Um, I hope you've been
getting my messages.

56:20.631 --> 56:23.926
I'm in California right now,
but I'm coming to London tomorrow.

56:24.510 --> 56:25.844
Hi, Jodi.

56:26.345 --> 56:27.638
Hi.

56:27.721 --> 56:29.097
Um…

56:29.181 --> 56:31.934
I'm so happy to be
finally speaking with you.

56:32.017 --> 56:35.187
I understand that you once worked
for Harvey Weinstein

56:35.270 --> 56:37.147
in the London office of Miramax.

56:37.231 --> 56:38.482
Is that right?

56:40.234 --> 56:41.360
Laura?

56:42.569 --> 56:44.321
[Laura crying]

56:48.325 --> 56:49.326
Laura…

56:49.993 --> 56:50.994
[sighs]

56:51.620 --> 56:53.163
Can I do anything to help?

56:53.789 --> 56:56.542
No. I can't talk about this right now.

56:56.625 --> 56:57.793
[line clicks]

57:05.968 --> 57:07.845
[child] We're tied.
You have the same pieces as me.

57:09.763 --> 57:11.515
Hey.

57:11.598 --> 57:13.725
Hey, my love. Come here.

57:17.187 --> 57:18.397
Hey, now.

57:19.898 --> 57:21.692
It's going to be all right.

57:22.401 --> 57:25.487
-It's going to be all right.
