57:25.571 --> 57:26.864
[child sniffling]

57:56.018 --> 57:57.019
[waiter] Here we are.

58:00.147 --> 58:01.148
Tea.

58:02.316 --> 58:03.358
Thank you.

58:05.027 --> 58:06.820
[chattering]

58:22.336 --> 58:24.755
You know, other people have tried
to write this story.

58:24.838 --> 58:26.131
He kills it every time.

58:26.215 --> 58:27.966
We're aware of that.

58:29.384 --> 58:31.512
And we're not gonna
let that happen to us.

58:35.891 --> 58:37.392
Are you okay, Zelda?

58:37.476 --> 58:38.519
Yes.

58:40.270 --> 58:41.271
So,

58:42.648 --> 58:44.566
you started working at Miramax
when you were 21?

58:44.650 --> 58:47.528
Yes.
I was an assistant at the London office.

58:48.195 --> 58:49.446
And how was it?

58:49.530 --> 58:50.822
It was great,

58:50.906 --> 58:53.242
but it would shift
when Harvey came to town.

58:53.325 --> 58:54.868
In what way?

58:54.952 --> 58:58.205
