59:06.505 --> 59:07.881
Like?

59:07.965 --> 59:12.052
For instance, I would have to go
to his hotel and wake Harvey up.

59:12.886 --> 59:15.973
Run a shower for him.
Get him out of bed.

59:16.056 --> 59:17.683
He would usually be naked.

59:17.766 --> 59:19.643
And he might try
to pull me onto him.

59:20.352 --> 59:22.980
-What did you do?
-Fend him off.

59:23.063 --> 59:25.440
I found humor
or aggression worked best.

59:26.149 --> 59:29.403
Harvey was either excited or furious.

59:29.945 --> 59:31.572
You never knew which it would be.

59:32.614 --> 59:35.868
Did anyone on the team
give you advice about him?

59:35.951 --> 59:37.244
Yes. [chuckles]

59:37.327 --> 59:40.539
Once, one girl told me
to always wear my puffer jacket,

59:40.622 --> 59:43.333
and to always sit in an armchair,

59:43.417 --> 59:45.460
never the sofa next to him,

59:45.544 --> 59:46.837
which helped.

59:47.838 --> 59:50.799
And that's how I knew
that it wasn't only happening to me.

59:52.009 --> 59:53.927
What was happening exactly?

59:54.011 --> 59:55.012
Bullying.

59:55.929 --> 59:57.097
Emotional abuse.

59:58.015 --> 59:59.892
I was just too young
to understand it.

1:00:01.351 --> 1:00:03.937
Harvey wanted people
to submit to him.

1:00:04.021 --> 1:00:05.022
And if they didn't?

1:00:05.105 --> 1:00:07.399
Well, then he'd roar. And he'd spit.

1:00:08.150 --> 1:00:09.985
He could destroy someone in seconds.

1:00:11.570 --> 1:00:12.905
Were you scared of him?

1:00:13.989 --> 1:00:16.241
Yes. We all were.

1:00:19.411 --> 1:00:21.580
So, three years into this,

1:00:21.663 --> 1:00:23.749
