-Sit.
-[sobbing]

1:01:20.597 --> 1:01:22.766
-[Zelda] And I held her.
-What is it?

1:01:23.725 --> 1:01:26.436
Did she tell you
what he did?

1:01:28.021 --> 1:01:29.106
Not exactly.

1:01:29.857 --> 1:01:31.525
Only that no one must know.

1:01:31.608 --> 1:01:32.693
But I knew.

1:01:33.235 --> 1:01:34.820
I knew that he must've…

1:01:36.989 --> 1:01:38.282
What?

1:01:38.365 --> 1:01:40.033
She was so upset.

1:01:40.742 --> 1:01:44.037
I knew that it had to be
the worst possible thing.

1:01:45.831 --> 1:01:48.292
I calmed her down,
and I went straight to confront Harvey.

1:01:48.876 --> 1:01:51.378
He was in a meeting with Scorsese,

1:01:52.129 --> 1:01:54.756
who hated him,
so it was a really big deal for Harvey.

1:01:55.299 --> 1:01:57.342
And I went straight up to him,

1:01:57.426 --> 1:02:01.054
and I said very clearly,
"You need to come with me right now."

1:02:01.138 --> 1:02:03.056
You went right up to them
and confronted him?

1:02:03.140 --> 1:02:05.267
Yeah. I was so angry.

1:02:05.934 --> 1:02:07.644
And in front of everyone,

1:02:07.728 --> 1:02:09.980
