1:02:39.927 --> 1:02:43.305
We came back to London.
We both resigned.

1:02:43.388 --> 1:02:44.890
I told my direct superior,

1:02:44.973 --> 1:02:48.185
who suggested we get ourselves
a good lawyer.

1:02:49.102 --> 1:02:50.896
I had no idea where to get one.

1:02:50.979 --> 1:02:53.232
I found a company
close to the office.

1:02:53.315 --> 1:02:55.359
And then I thought
it would be simple.

1:02:55.442 --> 1:02:56.818
Criminal proceedings.

1:02:56.902 --> 1:02:58.820
But our lawyer said
we had no chance

1:02:58.904 --> 1:03:00.989
and the only thing to do
was to agree to a settlement.

1:03:01.073 --> 1:03:02.407
And I said categorically no,

1:03:02.491 --> 1:03:05.619
that no money should change hands
and that we just wanted to stop him.

1:03:05.702 --> 1:03:07.663
And no UK police were involved?

1:03:07.746 --> 1:03:09.248
We had no case.

1:03:09.331 --> 1:03:12.251
We had no evidence
and no police report from Venice.

1:03:12.334 --> 1:03:15.921
And, you see, with rape, it is impossibly
difficult to get a prosecution.

1:03:16.004 --> 1:03:19.341
And the lawyers kept saying
damage limitation was the only way to go.

1:03:19.424 --> 1:03:23.470
So I said, "All right, then.
We have our own very real demands."

1:03:23.554 --> 1:03:26.306
Conditions that Harvey would have to meet
if we were to sign.

1:03:26.390 --> 1:03:28.016
And what were those conditions?

1:03:28.100 --> 1:03:31.395
We demanded that if Harvey had
another settlement within two years,

1:03:31.478 --> 1:03:34.231
that it had to be reported to Disney
or else he would be fired.

1:03:34.857 --> 1:03:36.859
Another was that
he would go to therapy,

1:03:36.942 --> 1:03:40.112
with me present initially,
so that he couldn't lie to the therapist.

1:03:40.195 --> 1:03:44.992
We demanded that HR would put in a system
to protect the women and staff.

1:03:45.075 --> 1:03:48.412
And it felt like
if we could achieve all of those,

1:03:48.495 --> 1:03:50.497
then that's what our silence
was paying for.

1:03:50.581 --> 1:03:53.166
That we were paying for him to stop.

1:03:54.710 --> 1:03:55.961
So we signed.

1:03:56.670 --> 1:03:59.006
And they had their own
insane conditions for us.

1:03:59.715 --> 1:04:00.966
What were they?

1:04:02.467 --> 1:04:05.721
I tried to commit them to memory.
They wouldn't give us our own copy.

1:04:05.804 --> 1:04:06.930
What?

1:04:07.014 --> 1:04:09.474
I was only given visitation rights
to my own settlement.

1:04:09.558 --> 1:04:10.642
That's in--

1:04:12.186 --> 1:04:13.353
That's incredible.

1:04:13.979 --> 1:04:15.689
But you memorized them?

1:04:16.940 --> 1:04:18.775
I asked for letters, too,

1:04:18.859 --> 1:04:21.862
