1:05:08.075 --> 1:05:09.493
It was horrible.

1:05:11.912 --> 1:05:13.247
What did you do then?

1:05:13.872 --> 1:05:15.666
I went to visit a friend in Guatemala,

1:05:16.291 --> 1:05:17.668
